<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.5">
<l>vaṅka mākaṭal vaṇṇaṉmā maṇi vaṇṇaṉ viṇṇavar kōṉmatu malart</l>
<l>toṅkal nīṇmuṭi yāṉneṭi yāṉpaṭi kaṭantāṉ</l>
<l>maṅkul tōymaṇi māṭaveṇ koṭi māka mītuyarn tēṟivā ṉuyar</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷ tāṉaṇa vuntiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He the hue of the great, wavy sea, the hue of a dark jewel, the celestials’ king,</l>
<l>The one with a tall crown with a honeyed flower garland, the tall one,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who surpassed the earth,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr where the moon, high in the sky, ascends</l>
<l>Climbing, rising above the space with white flags on jeweled mansions,</l>
<l rend="indent">which touch the clouds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
